      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breast portions</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until browned</p>",
